title: Trippy Taco
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Mexican
description: Quick service Mexican food with dairy-free variations of cheese and sour cream available. Menu includes tacos, burritos, quesadillas, nachos, breakfast burritos described as corn tortilla madness and Nutella and banana in a flour tortilla. Can make some dishes gluten-free upon request. Beverages are Inca cola and beverages imported from Central and South America, Mexican beer and mixed drinks. This outlet is behind Prince of Wales Hotel.
